<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Bex App - Milton Nano Technologies</title>

<style>

body{
font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
margin:0;
background:#081421;
color:white;
overflow-x:hidden;
}

/* Moving Tech Background */

body::before{
content:"";
position:fixed;
width:200%;
height:200%;
background:radial-gradient(circle,#00d4ff22 1px, transparent 1px);
background-size:40px 40px;
animation:moveTech 20s linear infinite;
z-index:-1;
}

@keyframes moveTech{
0%{transform:translate(0,0);}
100%{transform:translate(-200px,-200px);}
}

/* Header */

header{
background:#102c44;
padding:30px;
text-align:center;
}

.logo{
width:220px;
margin-bottom:10px;
}

header h1{
color:#00d4ff;
margin:5px;
}

/* Navigation */

nav{
text-align:center;
background:#0b1b2b;
padding:10px;
}

nav a{
color:white;
margin:15px;
text-decoration:none;
font-weight:bold;
}

/* Hero */

.hero{
text-align:center;
padding:70px 20px;
}

.hero h2{
font-size:34px;
color:#00d4ff;
}

/* Download Button */

.download-btn{
display:inline-block;
margin-top:20px;
padding:15px 30px;
background:#00d4ff;
color:black;
font-weight:bold;
border-radius:30px;
text-decoration:none;
transition:0.3s;
}

.download-btn:hover{
background:white;
transform:scale(1.1);
}

/* Cards */

.container{
max-width:1000px;
margin:auto;
padding:20px;
}

.card{
background:#132f48;
padding:25px;
border-radius:12px;
margin-top:20px;
}

/* Gallery */

.gallery{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
gap:20px;
margin-top:20px;
}

.gallery img{
width:100%;
border-radius:10px;
transition:0.5s;
}

.gallery img:hover{
transform:scale(1.05);
}

/* Floating Nano Particles */

.particle{
position:fixed;
width:6px;
height:6px;
background:#00d4ff;
border-radius:50%;
animation:float 8s infinite linear;
opacity:0.6;
}

@keyframes float{
0%{
transform:translateY(100vh);
}
100%{
transform:translateY(-10vh);
}
}

/* Footer */

footer{
background:#081421;
text-align:center;
padding:15px;
margin-top:40px;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<!-- Floating particles -->
<div class="particle" style="left:10%; animation-delay:0s;"></div>
<div class="particle" style="left:30%; animation-delay:2s;"></div>
<div class="particle" style="left:50%; animation-delay:4s;"></div>
<div class="particle" style="left:70%; animation-delay:1s;"></div>
<div class="particle" style="left:90%; animation-delay:3s;"></div>

<header>

<img src="bex-logo.jpg" class="logo">

<h1>BEX</h1>
<p>The Official App by Milton Nano Technologies</p>

</header>

<nav>
<a href="#">Home</a>
<a href="#">About</a>
<a href="#">Technology</a>
<a href="#">Contact</a>
</nav>

<section class="hero">

<h2>Welcome to Bex</h2>
<p>Innovating the future through nanotechnology.</p>

<a href="#" class="download-btn">Download Bex</a>

</section>

<div class="container">

<div class="card">

<h2>About Milton Nano Technologies</h2>

<p>
My name is Anome Lime, and I’m here to tell you about a company called Milton,
a leader in nanotechnology—the science of working with materials at a scale
so tiny that it’s measured in billionths of a meter.
</p>

<p>
Milton focuses on creating smart, powerful, and efficient solutions using
extremely small particles and devices. Their work helps improve medicine,
electronics, energy, and even everyday products we use at home and in school.
</p>

<p>
<b>Why is Milton important?</b><br>
Because nanotechnology is the future. It makes devices faster, medicines more
effective, and technology safer and more reliable. Milton is committed to
innovation, education, and inspiring young minds—like all of us here—to
think bigger by thinking smaller.
</p>

</div>

<div class="card">

<h2>Nanotechnology Visuals</h2>

<div class="gallery">

<img src="nano1.jpg">

